# 2. 異国の出会い

An: Sorry, I'm late, you two! I realized that I forgot my wallet when I was already in the elevator!
Akito: Seriously, good job forgetting your wallet when we're going shopping. You wouldn't have gotten much done.
Toya: I'm glad you noticed before we left. Anyway, now that we're all here, shall we?
Kohane: I'm so excited for this flea market. It's one of the most famous ones in New York, right?
An: Yup! We gotta thank our lucky stars that it's being held at the same time as SONIC NOTES! And it's right by the event venue too.
Toya: The event begins in the evening, so we should be able to take our time browsing.
Toya: Miku said she'd come visit later, so I hope she also gets to have some fun.
Kohane: Me too. Oh, a right at this corner and...
Kohane: Huh?
Kohane: Why are all those people gathered around?
An: Hmm... I hear music. Does that mean someone's singing?
Akito: But that's a huge crowd. Who's singing?
