Kohane: (Wow...)
Kohane: (This power... I'm feeling their voices in my gut.)
Kohane: (Not only that...)
Audience: “Hey, there they are! Over there!”
Audience: “You were right. I can't believe they're here. We really get to hear illys sing!”
??? & ???: ♪————————————!!
Kohane: illys...
Toya: It sounds like they're pretty well-known around these parts.
An: They sound amazing...! Wanna get a little closer, you guys?
Akito: Hey, no need to rush...
Akito: But I also wanna hear more.
???: ♪——————...
