Audience: “Whoa, that girl... She looks all timid, but she's got some real pipes!”
Audience: “Haha. I can't wait to see how those two from illys respond!”
Elena & Rebecca: ♪————————! ♪————————!
Kohane: (...! They really are amazing...)
Kohane: (I knew it when I heard them earlier...)
Kohane: (But these two sing at such a high level!)
Elena & Rebecca: ♪——! ——! ——~~~~! ♪————~~! ——————!!
Kohane: (The way they create a rhythm and modulate their voices... What they're doing is really complicated, but they make it look so easy.)
Kohane: (It's proof of how refined their technique is!)
Kohane: (Not only that...)
Elena & Rebecca: ♪————————! ♪————————!
Kohane: (They look like they're having so much fun!)
Kohane: (I can tell that Elena and Becky both really love to sing.)
Kohane: (And I know how they feel.)
Kohane: (Because I really love to sing too!)
