Rebecca: It's been a while since we got that pumped up!
Kohane: I couldn't resist going all-out, either!
Elena: Haha. That's good to hear!
Rebecca: Sorry about that, you guys. Thanks for letting us borrow your teammate.
Toya: No, that's okay. We were moved by your heartfelt performance.
An: That was so awesome! It was like you grabbed hold of my heart and shook it around like crazy...
Akito: Yeah. I was about ready to get up there with you.
Elena: Whoa, I wasn't expecting to get showered with so much praise! That's so kind of all of you♪
Rebecca: Let's sing again sometime if we get the chance. We like to perform here from time to time.
Rebecca: Next time, let's all sing together.
Kohane: Thank you!
Elena: Anyway, thanks again! See you later!
Toya: They blew through here like a storm...
Akito: Yeah. But man, they were incredible singers.
Akito: Especially the older one... She felt so free while she sang.
An: Becky's technique was also really amazing! She did a bunch of tricky things, but made everything look so easy. I was totally entranced.
An: And you looked like you had a blast too, Kohane.
Kohane: I did! I could tell exactly what they were feeling, and things just kept getting more fun as we sang.
Toya: I see.
Kohane: (I got to see something new again...)
Kohane: (Those two said that they sing here from time to time, so I hope we run into them again before we leave the US...!)
